WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.564
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.564 --> 00:00:05.303
I just have a video I want to do for you all today.

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:14.133
I've been praying and asking the Lord what he's wanting me to talk to you about, and I have a direction I think I need to go.

00:00:14.386 --> 00:00:17.639
The next two things I'm going to tell you about were open-eyed visions.

00:00:17.639 --> 00:00:24.505
When I was praying—just like I am right here in this chair right now—all of a sudden the Lord opened a portal above me.

00:00:24.505 --> 00:00:29.639
I saw a massive portal open because I just asked him, 'How's your day today, Lord?

00:00:30.119 --> 00:00:31.400
What were you about?

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:32.387
What were you doing today?

00:00:32.387 --> 00:00:44.093
' I was just curious, talking to him like I normally do, and all of a sudden he said, 'Brandon, I'll show you what I was doing,' and he opened up a portal over my living room.

00:00:44.700 --> 00:01:03.320
I saw him—and this is pretty cool—getting our table ready for our banquet: massive tables for a reception for us when we come home.

00:01:04.074 --> 00:01:10.640
Every plate was so perfect, but every plate was different.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:20.840
One was a flower, but my plate that was in front of me, he showed me in the spirit realm.

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:29.586
I looked up and I could see the tables, and the plates were perfect.

00:01:30.610 --> 00:01:35.613
It was a perfect lily, but it was almost transparent.

00:01:40.707 --> 00:01:41.940
It was red and it had all the beautiful designs on this plate.

00:01:41.940 --> 00:01:53.467
On the plate was a name card, and my name was written on the plate as a reserved seat for me for this banquet that we will partake in when the Rapture of the church happens.

00:02:07.131 --> 00:02:07.520
This is one of the first things that happens: I saw a banquet, a party he has for us.

00:02:11.298 --> 00:02:12.151
It is a massive celebration of us coming home.

00:02:20.588 --> 00:02:29.621
All of the plates were perfect, like I said, and then we had these glasses, and all the glasses were this fine crystal that I've never seen on this Earth before.

00:02:30.239 --> 00:02:36.439
The glasses were beautiful, and you could see the forks, and the forks were perfect.

00:02:48.326 --> 00:02:48.629
They had all the forks lined up, and they had a napkin, the plates, and all the beautiful place setting.

00:02:48.629 --> 00:03:01.600
You could see the people that I was familiar with from this Earth—my friends, the people that I know are born again.

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:16.160
My wife had her place next to me, and other people that I love, like family members, had their name tags in their reserved plates all around us.

00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:29.503
I could see directly around me all the beautiful things, but everybody's stuff was personalized to them.

00:03:29.503 --> 00:03:43.780
It wasn't just one type of plate or one type of glass; it was personalized to the desires of your heart, what was inside of you.

00:03:49.199 --> 00:03:49.679
It was beautiful what he had done.

00:03:52.119 --> 00:04:05.225
In the centers of the table were these flower arrangements that were the most beautiful flower arrangements: lilies, white roses, and they had this tulle.

00:04:08.139 --> 00:04:13.200
There was drapery all coming out of these trees.

00:04:16.871 --> 00:04:29.480
There were trees—and I don't know where these trees came from—like these huge, massive oak trees like you would see in Louisiana at those plantation houses.

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:42.770
It was an outside area, not in a building or a palace.

00:04:42.770 --> 00:04:44.320
This reception is outside.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:51.815
There was green grass all around, and there were beautiful trees all covering the top.

00:05:02.166 --> 00:05:02.549
There was drapery all coming down from these trees all underneath where the banquet's at.

00:05:02.549 --> 00:05:16.486
There were diamond-like beads and pearls hanging out of the trees, all fastened with the tulle, all this beautiful white silk and mesh; the pearls were wrapped in it.

00:05:17.777 --> 00:05:24.583
It was gold, and you could see all the colors.

00:05:27.340 --> 00:05:34.914
It was draped and it was so decorated—so perfect—it was like a wedding reception.

00:05:34.914 --> 00:05:38.225
Everything was just immaculate and gorgeous.

00:05:38.510 --> 00:05:43.425
I try to capture and tell you everything the Lord showed me.

00:05:43.425 --> 00:05:50.420
There were some kind of little lights—and this sounds really weird—like twinkle lights inside of the tulle and the pearls.

00:05:50.420 --> 00:05:51.954
It was absolutely gorgeous.

00:05:51.954 --> 00:05:58.874
Everything—the place settings, the vases with flowers, and everything—it was so precious, his celebration for us when we come home.

00:05:58.874 --> 00:06:04.900
This is another time I was praying; these were two different times.

00:06:06.116 --> 00:06:08.470
Again, I always ask the Lord, 'How's your day today?

00:06:08.470 --> 00:06:10.476
How are things going?

00:06:10.476 --> 00:06:13.560
' just like I'm talking to a friend.

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:19.661
He's my best friend, so it's like talking to your friend on the telephone.

00:06:19.661 --> 00:06:23.440
I always ask, 'How's your day today?

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:26.986
What did you do today?

00:06:26.986 --> 00:06:31.338
' or like you talk to your spouse.

00:06:31.338 --> 00:06:37.800
I asked how his day was—'How was your day today?

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:40.753
What all went on?

00:06:40.753 --> 00:06:49.520
'—and all of a sudden he said, 'Hi, Brandon,' and he started talking to me again.

00:06:52.306 --> 00:06:54.500
He said, 'I want to show you what we're doing today.

00:06:54.500 --> 00:07:00.279
' He said they're having a reception practice, a parade practice.

00:07:04.175 --> 00:07:11.039
He said, 'When you come home in the Rapture, son, we are going to have a massive home-welcoming party for you.

00:07:11.039 --> 00:07:28.079
' Everybody that has died before you, they're waiting for you, and we are going to celebrate all the people—this massive amount of the church that is coming home in the Rapture.

00:07:28.079 --> 00:07:32.660
He said we're going to have a massive parade.

00:07:32.660 --> 00:07:39.690
It's a reception, but I could see the people and they had banners.

00:07:39.690 --> 00:08:10.215
He showed me what they were doing: Jesus was riding a white horse, and he was the head of the reception of what they were practicing, and all the people kept saying, 'For the Lord is good, and his mercy endureth forever,' as he was riding on this horse in heaven.

00:08:10.215 --> 00:08:15.300
I could see the streets of gold.

00:08:15.300 --> 00:08:24.953
I could see the people on both sides of the streets, just like the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade.

00:08:24.953 --> 00:08:35.514
Both sides of the street had people all lining the way; it looked like a massive town, like a city.

00:08:38.399 --> 00:08:47.135
I could see buildings on both sides—massive buildings all beautifully designed, kind of like you would see in Europe, with old English-style tile roofs.

00:08:47.135 --> 00:08:51.514
It was beautiful, like a downtown area in heaven.

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:07.000
I could see the people, and Jesus was riding on the gold street on his horse, and people had those kingly banners that said 'King of Kings' and 'Lord of Lords.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:14.439
' All the banners were going down the street, and people were celebrating and rejoicing.

00:09:14.439 --> 00:09:26.891
This is going to sound really crazy, but there was gold confetti in the air, and people were celebrating.

00:09:26.891 --> 00:09:32.290
They were practicing, getting ready for the coming of the church.

00:09:45.111 --> 00:09:45.399
He said, 'We're getting ready for you, son.

00:09:45.399 --> 00:09:48.457
We're getting ready for the church!

00:09:48.457 --> 00:09:59.700
' I got so excited because I could see all the people rejoicing, and they kept saying, 'For he is good, and his mercy endures forever.

00:09:59.700 --> 00:10:19.679
' I could hear all the people, and he was riding his horse.

00:10:31.177 --> 00:10:31.720
His horse had a bridle that was covered in jewels.

00:10:56.417 --> 00:10:56.829
His horse was beautiful and had a chest piece with beautiful diamonds, emeralds, sapphires, and rubies.

00:11:15.252 --> 00:11:15.821
He was riding his horse through the town, being worshipped in heaven.

00:11:38.936 --> 00:11:43.639
I was just in awe of how much he loves us, how much he cares, and all the personal detail he takes the time just to love on his people.

00:11:43.639 --> 00:12:01.138
People have no idea how much Jesus loves you and how much he takes thought for every detail, from the plates to the forks to the parade.

00:12:01.138 --> 00:12:05.014
He's so excited for his children to come home.

00:12:05.014 --> 00:12:18.444
He's waiting on us, and when God says 'Go,' he's coming back for us, and we're going to rule and reign with him forever and ever.

00:12:18.444 --> 00:12:21.709
For the King, he is good.

00:12:21.709 --> 00:12:27.920
Jesus is good, and his mercy endures forever.

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:32.460
There was a bridge with a huge river going through it.

00:12:41.829 --> 00:12:42.604
The town was right here on this side, and the gold street went over this bridge.

00:12:46.994 --> 00:12:47.720
There was a river flowing out of the throne—Living Water.

00:12:50.820 --> 00:13:06.480
There were steps that went up after this huge bridge over the river, there was green on both sides, and there was this beautiful castle-looking building where he was riding his horse.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:10.160
All the people were there in their gowns.

00:13:10.160 --> 00:13:22.425
This is what's really amazing too: everyone worshipping him on those horses had different gowns; not one gown or robe was the same.

00:13:35.800 --> 00:13:35.980
There were different colors—everyone thinks it's just white gowns, but there were robes with colors.

00:13:35.980 --> 00:13:44.102
Some people had robes and some had gowns, but there were more gowns than robes.

00:13:44.493 --> 00:13:54.620
It looked like a lot of people just had a gown of salvation; they were just born again and had a revelation of getting saved.

00:13:59.071 --> 00:14:30.930
The people who had robes had beautiful colors with emblems and things of honor for what you did on the earth for him.

00:14:36.352 --> 00:14:36.804
There were thick, beautiful robes.

00:14:36.804 --> 00:14:46.535
I couldn't see the people's faces because they were facing away, their backs toward me.

00:14:46.863 --> 00:14:58.580
On the other side of the street, I could see the people a little bit, and they were all lining the streets.

00:14:58.580 --> 00:15:03.869
I look forward to it: the peace, the presence.

00:15:03.869 --> 00:15:05.210
Oh, Jesus.

00:15:05.210 --> 00:15:20.059
I take myself back when I talk about it; I can feel the feeling I had when I saw him on his horse.

00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:29.499
He had a crown on that was beautiful and towered above his head, covered in really cool jewels.

00:15:30.515 --> 00:15:30.750
It was gorgeous.

00:15:30.750 --> 00:15:38.000
This crown had a purple banner around the bottom of it with stuff like fur.

00:15:39.886 --> 00:15:53.019
He had a cape on with a gold medallion in the middle, and his cape draped down by his legs while he was on his horse.

00:15:53.019 --> 00:15:56.453
Everything was just so perfect.

00:15:56.453 --> 00:16:04.159
So, Father, I thank you right now in the name of Jesus.

00:16:04.159 --> 00:16:20.777
I'm going to do a blanket prayer for all the people that have asked for help, all the prayer needs, the healings, and the people whose loved ones are far away from the Lord.

00:16:20.777 --> 00:16:22.151
Father, we thank you.

00:16:22.323 --> 00:16:31.656
Lord, you showed me in a vision today little birds chirping in a mama's nest, and they are asking, 'Help, help, help!

00:16:31.656 --> 00:16:33.343
Cheep, cheep, cheep!

00:16:33.343 --> 00:16:45.919
' I saw them in the spirit, Lord, and I said, 'God, there are so many mouths to feed; I can't do it all.

00:16:45.919 --> 00:16:50.507
' You said to me, 'It's my job, Brandon.

00:17:07.863 --> 00:17:08.109
The Holy Spirit will take care of this,' and I saw that big bird dump a whole bunch of worms on those little babies.

00:17:08.109 --> 00:17:17.183
Today, I pray that for you: the Holy Spirit is going to meet your every need right where you're at.

00:17:25.632 --> 00:17:29.715
Jesus has got this for you.

00:17:30.050 --> 00:17:35.200
I call healing over your bodies and deliverance over you in Jesus' name.

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:37.880
I call restoration over your marriages.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I call blessing over your home financially.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.100
Father, I pray the Lord would bless them and keep them; may his face shine upon you and be gracious to you and give you peace.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.150
I call those blessings over their home in Jesus' name, and we praise the Lord for everything he's already done and what he continues to do in your life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
In the name of Jesus, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Jesus loves you, and I love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
I'm so thankful that you're a part of my family here.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
